  <releases>
    <release version="0.1.0" date="2021-12-30">
      <description>
        <p>The very first release of File Shredder. It supports progress tracking, and
					boasts a GNOME compliant interface.</p>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.0.0.alpha1" date="2022-6-30">
      <description>
      <p>A significant rewite of File Shredder with the added capability to shred thumb drives.
      Among other changes are:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Added checking so a file cannot be loaded twice</li>
          <li>Handy list for thumb drives on open button</li>
          <li>Smooth progress tracking</li>
          <li>Written using GTK4 and Adwaita</li>
          <li>Desktop notifications are shown if the window is not focused</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
